station hand
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:an assistant worker on a sheep and/or cattle station [as distinct from a shepherd or musterer.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
